actical, this book contains a wealth of concrete examples of curriculum design and teaching techniques structured to appeal specifically to children in their middle school years.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 22. Okt 2019) 7aEDUCATION / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780226244136423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780226244136.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aEBA_FAO